<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Шаблон сайта</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
	<div class="wrapper">
		<header class="header">
			<div class="container"></div>
		</header>
		<main class="main">
			<section class="intro">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="intro__cards">
						<div class="intro__card">
							<div class="intro__icon">
								<img src="./img/svg/icons-1.svg" alt="/">
							</div>
							<h2>Enhanced website security</h2>
							<p>We'll help you identify and eliminate vulnerabilities in your website's security to prevent attacks and site downtime.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="intro__card">
							<div class="intro__icon">
								<img src="./img/svg/icons-2.svg" alt="/">
							</div>
							<h2>Time and cost savings</h2>
							<p>Security testing can help you avoid potential problems in the future, saving you time and money on fixing issues that may arise from attacks.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="intro__card">
							<div class="intro__icon">
								<img src="./img/svg/icons-3.svg" alt="/">
							</div>
							<h2>Experienced experts</h2>
							<p>Our security specialists have years of experience and professional skills to help protect your website.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="intro__card">
							<div class="intro__icon">
								<img src="./img/svg/icons-4.svg" alt="/">
							</div>
							<h2>Confidentiality and security</h2>
							<p>We guarantee complete confidentiality and data protection, so you can be sure your website is secure.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
	</div>
</body>
</html>